■Columbia, New York, Fordham, Tulane (USA) 
■University of Michigan Law School (USA)
■Osgoode Hall (Canada) 
■Bergen (Norway) 
■Bologna (Italy) 
■Paris I, Pierre Mendez, Nice-Antipolis (France) 
■Freie Universität Berlin (Germany) 
■ULB (Belgium) 
■Copenhagen (Denmark) 
■Kent and Essex (UK) 
■Autónoma Madrid, Barcelona (Spain) 
■Cape Town and Potchefstroom (South Africa). 
